336
00:25:14,832 --> 00:25:15,912
<font color="#ffff80"><b>Bagus sekali.</b></font>

337
00:25:16,432 --> 00:25:17,312
<font color="#ffff80"><b>Aku mengagumimu.</b></font>

338
00:25:17,392 --> 00:25:18,392
