342
00:25:32,472 --> 00:25:33,552
<font color="#ffff80"><b><i>"Aku mencintaimu."</i></b></font>

343
00:25:33,992 --> 00:25:36,392
<font color="#ffff80"><b><i>Kenapa aku selalu mengacaukannya
