344
00:25:37,952 --> 00:25:38,952
<font color="#ffff80"><b>Oke, tidak masalah.</b></font>

345
00:25:40,272 --> 00:25:41,232
<font color="#ffff80"><b>Shancai?</b></font>

346
00:25:44,632 --> 00:25:45,992
<font color="#ffff80"><b>Baiklah. Hentikan omong kosong itu.</b></font>

347
00:25:46,152 --> 00:25:46,992
<font color="#ffff80"><b>Dah.</b></font>

348
00:25:48,352 --> 00:25:50,032
<font color="#ffff80"><b>Siapa itu? Kenapa kamu menyebut namaku?</b></font>

349
00:25:50,752 --> 00:25:52,992
<font color="#ffff80"><b>Ximen bilang dia akan
