350
00:25:53,272 --> 00:25:54,992
<font color="#ffff80"><b>di rumahnya.</b></font>

351
00:25:55,352 --> 00:25:56,312
<font color="#ffff80"><b>Kamu diundang.</b></font>

352
00:25:56,872 --> 00:25:58,112
<font color="#ffff80"><b>Pesta Mencicipi Teh Nasional?</b></font>

353
00:25:59,472 --> 00:26:00,952
<font color="#ffff80"><b>Temanmu juga diundang.</b></font>

354
00:26:01,592 --> 00:26:02,472
<font color="#ffff80"><b>Xiaoyou?</b></font>

355
00:26:02,952 --> 00:26:05,312
<font color="#ffff80"><b>Apa Ximen akan ada di sana?</b></font>

356
00:26:07,352 --> 00:26:10,112
<font color="#ffff80"><b>Pestanya ada di rumahnya.
