364
00:26:44,832 --> 00:26:45,872
<font color="#ffff80"><b>Aku mengerti.</b></font>

365
00:26:45,992 --> 00:26:49,032
<font color="#ffff80"><b>Apa pendapatmu tentang budaya teh?</b></font>

366
00:26:49,112 --> 00:26:50,472
<font color="#ffff80"><b>Karena teman baikku, Ximen,</b></font>

367
00:26:50,552 --> 00:26:52,992
