369
00:26:57,432 --> 00:26:59,192
<font color="#ffff80"><b>Aku mengenalnyaa dengan baik.</b></font>

370
00:26:59,272 --> 00:27:00,912
<font color="#ffff80"><b>Jenis teh apa yang kamu sukai?</b></font>

371
00:27:01,312 --> 00:27:03,992
<font color="#ffff80"><b>Teh hitam Assam, karena cukup unik.</b></font>

372
00:27:04,112 --> 00:27:07,312
