415
00:29:15,792 --> 00:29:17,792
<font color="#ffff80"><b>Tentu saja. Apa aku tidak terlihat seperti itu?</b></font>

416
00:29:31,152 --> 00:29:32,032
<font color="#ffff80"><b>Apa?</b></font>

417
00:29:33,512 --> 00:29:34,752
<font color="#ffff80"><b>Kamu juga harus berganti.</b></font>

418
00:29:35,472 --> 00:29:37,592
<font color="#ffff80"><b>Tetapi para ahli juga bisa melakukan kesalahan</b></font>

419
00:29:38,472 --> 00:29:39,312
<font color="#ffff80"><b>karena cheongsam</b></font>

420
00:29:40,392 --> 00:29:41,552
<font color="#ffff80"><b>tidak bisa dipakai oleh katak.</b></font>

421
00:29:42,152 --> 00:29:42,992
<font color="#ffff80"><b>Kamu...</b></font>

422
00:30:06,632 --> 00:30:07,472
<font color="#ffff80"><b>Ximen.</b></font>

423
00:30:09,392 --> 00:30:11,352
<font color="#ffff80"><b>Apa kamu biasanya mengadakan pertemuan seperti itu?</b></font>

424
00:30:12,632 --> 00:30:14,952
<font color="#ffff80"><b>Sesudah lulus, aku jarang
