425
00:30:21,352 --> 00:30:23,792
<font color="#ffff80"><b>Tapi, pinggangmu sangat besar.</b></font>

426
00:30:24,592 --> 00:30:27,272
<font color="#ffff80"><b>Mau apa kamu?
Aku adalah katak dengan pinggang besar. Terus?</b></font>

427
00:30:29,192 --> 00:30:31,352
<font color="#ffff80"><b>Jangan khawatir Si menyukaimu apa adanya.</b></font>

428
00:30:35,152 --> 00:30:36,152
<font color="#ffff80"><b>Ximen.</b></font>

429
00:30:37,592 --> 00:30:39,192
<font color="#ffff80"><b>Bisakah kamu berjanji padaku satu hal?</b></font>

430
00:30:41,072 --> 00:30:42,032
<font color="#ffff80"><b>Apa itu?</b></font>

431
00:30:44,712 --> 00:30:45,912
<font color="#ffff80"><b>Aku ingin berbicara</b></font>

432
00:30:46,752 --> 00:30:48,952
<font color="#ffff80"><b>- tentangmu dan Xiaoyou ...
