<font color="#ffff80"><b>Ketahuan.</b></font>

454
00:32:44,392 --> 00:32:45,712
<font color="#ffff80"><b>Hei, Li Zhen, kamu juga...</b></font>

455
00:32:46,272 --> 00:32:47,392
<font color="#ffff80"><b>Bertengkarlah lagi.</b></font>

