00:32:48,472 --> 00:32:49,672
<font color="#ffff80"><b>Jangan konyol.</b></font>

457
00:32:51,232 --> 00:32:53,312
<font color="#ffff80"><b>Sangat menyenangkan melihat Si dan Shancai berdebat.</b></font>

458
00:32:53,832 --> 00:32:56,552
